    riskFactors: ["Maternal GBS colonization without adequate intrapartum prophylaxis", "Premature rupture of membranes (PROM) >18 hours", "Prematurity (<37 weeks gestation)", "Maternal chorioamnionitis (fever, uterine tenderness, foul-smelling amniotic fluid)", "Low birth weight", "Maternal urinary tract infection with GBS", "Invasive fetal monitoring"],
