    riskFactors: ["Prematurity (<34 weeks gestation, highest risk factor)", "Maternal diabetes (hyperinsulinemia delays surfactant production)", "Cesarean delivery without labor (absence of catecholamine surge)", "Perinatal asphyxia", "Male sex", "Second-born twin", "Hypothermia at birth"],
